description.en:
Hamachi Finance is a multi-currency and multi-chain reward token. By buying and holding $HAMI users are farming rewards and accumulating tokens supported by the Hamachi Finance Protocol.

Hamachi will initially launch on Arbitrum and will later expand to other L2's
